response.original_title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: Wubbzy Goes Green
response.overview: Wow! Wow! Everyone in Wuzzleburg is getting involved in saving the planet! In these earth-friendly episodes, Wubbzy, Widget, Walden and Daizy must find a new place for the Wuzzle Bears to live, think up creative ways to reuse juice bottles and learn to grow their own doodleberries. Your pre-schooler will discover important lessons about ecology, harmony, and personal responsibility while enjoying plenty of singing and dancing!
response.title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: Wubbzy Goes Green
